    {
      "id": "PopularPost261268",
      "post_content": "@Boakes2047 and forumbrowser:  \nWell, if Grim Monolith would be replaced with [Simian Spirit Guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide), whole combo works, but if player would have this perfect draw of 7 cards in opening hand, it is almost as much probable as playing against opponent who has 2 [Gut Shot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gut Shot)s in hand as well. :-)  \n  \nHowever back to card. This is good combo fueling card, quite powerful and all, but I personally prefere its more ballanced brother, [Basalt Monolith](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Basalt Monolith). Does not suit to every deck, but in decks where it is, it shines out, because into such deck, it is put because of reason.",
      "posted_by": "spirit_of_blue",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost261268\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@Boakes2047 and  forumbrowser:<br/>Well, if Grim Monolith would be replaced with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Simian Spirit Guide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide\">Simian Spirit Guide</a>, whole combo works, but if player would have this perfect draw of 7 cards in opening hand, it is almost as much probable as playing against opponent who has 2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gut Shot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gut Shot\">Gut Shot</a>s in hand as well. :-)<br/><br/>However back to card. This is good combo fueling card, quite powerful and all, but I personally prefere its more ballanced brother, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Basalt Monolith\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Basalt Monolith\">Basalt Monolith</a>. Does not suit to every deck, but in decks where it is, it shines out, because into such deck, it is put because of reason.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '261268'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46413\">spirit_of_blue</span>\r\n                                (8/6/2012 2:37:14 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
