    {
      "id": "PopularPost333167",
      "post_content": "Forget about infinite mana combos. This thing alone gives you freakin' **six** mana on turn three! Remember [Primeval Titan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primeval Titan), once the dominating force of Standard? Those decks filled their whole deck with mana elves and ramp spells, and still the Titan usually came down turn four instead of three. [Pentad Prism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pentad Prism) was already extremely good, and this thing is 1.5x Pentad Prism at the same cost, even without considering combos like with [Voltaic Key](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voltaic Key), which is beyond absurd. Sure, I guess compared to Vintage staples like [Mishra's Workshop](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's Workshop) this isn't *that* broken...",
      "posted_by": "sweetgab",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost333167\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Forget about infinite mana combos. This thing alone gives you freakin' <b>six</b> mana on turn three! Remember <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Primeval Titan\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primeval Titan\">Primeval Titan</a>, once the dominating force of Standard? Those decks filled their whole deck with mana elves and ramp spells, and still the Titan usually came down turn four instead of three. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pentad Prism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pentad Prism\">Pentad Prism</a> was already extremely good, and this thing is 1.5x Pentad Prism at the same cost, even without considering combos like with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voltaic Key\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voltaic Key\">Voltaic Key</a>, which is beyond absurd. Sure, I guess compared to Vintage staples like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mishra's Workshop\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's Workshop\">Mishra's Workshop</a> this isn't <i>that</i> broken...</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '333167'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy98788\">sweetgab</span>\r\n         